      "title": "American Mah Jongg",
      "description": "<p>All playing levels welcome! We are an open, friendly group of experienced and newer players who play American Mah Jongg and follow NMJL rules. Please bring a current NMJL card with you. If you don&#8217;t have one, someone usually has an extra card to loan out. For more info email Stacey Rea:\u00a0<a href=\"mailto:stacey1955@gmail.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">stacey1955@gmail.com</a>.</p>",
