      "url": "https://www.themissingpiecegames.com/event/one-piece-op-17-release-event/",
      "rest_url": "https://www.themissingpiecegames.com/wp-json/tribe/events/v1/events/17077",
      "title": "One Piece OP-17 Release Event",
      "description": "<p>Welcome fellow pirates! Set a course to The Missing Piece to compete with fellow fans of the One Piece Card Game using the new cards in the latest set!</p>\n<p>5:30pm &#8211; In person sign ups begin. This is also a great time to get to know the other participants, get food or drinks from our amazing baristas, and pick up any supplies you may need for the event, such as sleeves!</p>\n<p>6:00pm &#8211; Deck building begins! Players will have 50 minutes to build a 40 card deck from the 6 booster packs provided! Remember, it is assumed that you have a Leader that is all colors, so you have no color restrictions when deck building.</p>\n<p>6:50pm &#8211; Round 1 pairings are announced. There will be three 30 minute rounds where players will compete in a best-of-one match!</p>\n<p>Around 8:30pm &#8211; Prizes are awarded! All players will receive promotional items for participating, with additional prizes based on their performance in the event!</p>",
